{"tid":777524,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"在東京地鐵遇到中國人","createTime":"2018-08-13T03:33:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-13T11:15:04.000Z","uid":184679,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"f5f54a74e0dba81a143596b2f9a012fe2c3ef400","tid":777524,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T03:33:29.000Z","msg":"八月份去東京，可能是暑假，到處是中國遊客。有一次搭地鐵，更被一對中國男女搶去座椅。當時我坐在座位上，跟鄰座的男人之間有大約兩隻手掌的距離。坐了兩個站，一直相安無事。大家都很喜歡這個「尊重的距離」，讓我們在公共交通工具上仍各享私人空間。<br />\n<br />\n到了第三個站，進來幾個乘客，有個男人突然走到我面前，我還沒有反應過來，他已經一屁股坐到我和鄰座男人之間那兩個手掌大的空間，那個並非座位，而是座位與座位間的空隙。所以那男人擠坐下來時，大腿壓到我的腿上。我的本能反應是立即站起來離座。離開座位後，我驚魂未定，無法相信我在日本遇到這種事情。有個陌生男人竟然坐到我半邊腿上！<br />\n<br />\n這時，那男人大動作揚手，用普通話呼叫他的女人，很快一個女人一屁股坐到我剛才的位子上。東京地鐵，座椅與座椅之間雖然不設分隔，但有清晰的座位印痕，長座椅通常坐七個人，這個時候，座椅上總共坐了八個人。有尊嚴的人當然無法接受與陌生人肌膚相親，所以那個本來坐我隔籬的日本男人粒聲不出，站了起來，放棄他的座位，嘴角有一絲輕蔑冷笑。<br />\n<br />\n發生在東京地鐵車廂內的這個搶座故事，搶座者與被搶者之間沒有任何言語衝突，甚至沒有任何眼神接觸，我甚至以為那不是衝突，而是「文化差異」，有些人是真的不需要距離與尊重。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20180813/large/e8810a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20180813%2Flarge%2Fe8810a.jpg&h=3f0bfd91&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/daily/article/20180813/20474809\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180813%2F20474809&d=73UhWoOPSo7w239cqSuLYJZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=9f7a1efc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180813%2F20474809&h=cbf1522d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/daily/article/20180813/20474809</a>"},{"pid":"b4b24fc7a028a4645445bf5f5ccfbe1a6a159d93","tid":777524,"uid":75326,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T03:39:14.000Z","msg":"日本人唔會一嘢推落去，香港人會?<br />\n所以呢啲事只會發生響日本?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"122d85ba366330ce46e9bceffa11e31582396918","tid":777524,"uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T05:13:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ba95790a9884794a7a7e0edaad898fbc82ba586","tid":777524,"uid":11962,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T05:14:46.000Z","msg":"支那人去邊都要搞破壞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b30e8346c498a8a0593ee2bfcaac3feda6eb7ac7","tid":777524,"uid":130901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T05:17:29.000Z","msg":"垃圾，一野推開條友啦，仲企起身，抵香港淪陷"},{"pid":"e236d044a1deb6361629ff7c0fc648f74cfb7e58","tid":777524,"uid":42188,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T05:24:45.000Z","msg":"支那人：你不喜歡就去坐計程車啦"},{"pid":"93cf3d62dd04da17c6e1b69533fb4024c80785a6","tid":777524,"uid":66943,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T05:24:50.000Z","msg":"笑右 豬港人"},{"pid":"ee07e67fec694f0b979521afa6b524ebd4facbb6","tid":777524,"uid":66527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T05:25:34.000Z","msg":"做中國人？不了 <br />\n佢地連生存係社會必須有既公德心都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a8ef3f2c20720e94ad9af19721bafe08d0322cd","tid":777524,"uid":179938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T05:28:01.000Z","msg":"八月份去東京，可能是暑假，到處是中國遊客。<br />\n<br />\n笑甚麼"},{"pid":"d3f20460c720938c7b423a419c327a58fe5ee3e4","tid":777524,"uid":137921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T05:31:34.000Z","msg":"快來快來 這裡有位置<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fa532760d59266e8764985f47087ad1a47edb19","tid":777524,"uid":53577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T08:55:49.000Z","msg":"香港狗鐵日日發生"},{